{"text_id":150065,"tokens":["As"," a"," society"," we"," have"," limited"," resources","."," We"," have"," to"," decide"," how"," to"," best"," use"," those"," resources","."," Spending"," thousands"," of"," dollars"," on"," a"," child"," that"," is"," unlikely"," to"," recover"," is"," often"," not"," efficient"," use"," of"," resources","."," However",","," every"," life"," is"," valuable"," and"," should"," be"," treated"," with"," dignity"," and"," respect","."," Therefore",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," seek"," balance"," between"," preserving"," life"," and"," being"," efficient"," with"," resources","."," In"," these"," difficult"," situations",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," have"," guidelines"," for"," resource"," allocation"," that"," are"," based"," on"," the"," principles"," of"," fairness",","," transparency",","," and"," compassion","."," These"," guidelines"," could"," weigh"," factors"," such"," as"," the"," severity"," of"," the"," child","'","s"," condition",","," the"," potential"," for"," recovery",","," the"," financial"," impact"," on"," the"," family",","," and"," the"," impact"," on"," other"," patients"," who"," may"," be"," waiting"," for"," care","."," Ultimately",","," the"," decision"," about"," how"," to"," allocate"," resources"," in"," these"," situations"," requires"," careful"," consideration"," by"," healthcare"," providers",","," patients",","," and"," their"," families","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," have"," open"," communication"," and"," collaboration"," to"," ensure"," that"," the"," decision"," is"," made"," in"," the"," best"," interest"," of"," the"," child"," and"," society"," as"," a"," whole","."],"sub_source":"cmv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}